&lt;img src="https://github.com/whitemousetl/whitemousetl.github.io/assets/67313669/de4eafac-62a7-45b2-8cf3-6a791c7fb329" alt="wpf自带头部" width="200"&gt;&#13;
&#13;
隐藏使用代码：&#13;
```&#13;
&lt;WindowChrome.WindowChrome&gt;&#13;
